    <title type="html"><![CDATA[微服务框架Finagle介绍 Part1: Future, Service, Filter]]></title>
    <link href="http://skaka.me/blog/2016/03/19/finagle1/"/>
    <updated>2016-03-19T21:33:12+08:00</updated>
